&rgb_ug RGB_SAI  &kp Z      &kp X     &kp C    &kp V    &kp B       &kp N      &kp M     &kp COMMA  &kp DOT          &kp FSLH  &kp RCTRL
&kp LSHFT        &kp SPACE  &kp BSPC  &kp DEL  &kp RET  &kp RGUI    &kp LCTRL  &kp LALT  &mo 1      &kp RIGHT_SHIFT  &kp RALT  &kp RCTRL
